Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.84,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Bounce, 高鳴る鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.62,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}No doubts, 感じる波動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.67,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}研ぎ澄ます感性を CONTROL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.08,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Like a 歌舞伎的 Playing a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.25,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}When you're in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.93,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}What's a Hero? Break the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.55,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}What's a Hero? Make new waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.75,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}That's a hero! Save all the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.70,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}You can be who you are & be free yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.86,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Is this where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.98,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}No no 終わらない Broken road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.07,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}続く Story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.24,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}信じるのは　自分の HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.56,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}大義より仁義　異論はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.70,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}BELIEVE IN YOURSELF
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.57,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}背負った誓い　歪ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.14,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}巻き起こせ　革命 REVOLUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.76,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}挑め世界　沈ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.74,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}舞い上がる　異端 NO IMITATION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.38,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}YOU AND I FEEL ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.86,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Overdrive It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.26,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}誰がヒーロー？ Break the old ways
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.16,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}お前がヒーロー！ MAKE NEW WAVES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.17,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.56,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.47,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.57,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! NOW LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:05.89,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}I've been walking all alone for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:12.84,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Witnessed fights and falls and never knew what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:19.88,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Searching for the answers but where am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:26.06,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Til the age of so much I have lost.
